  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.3.0-beta02\" data-text=\"Version 1.3.0-beta02\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.3.0-beta02</h3>\n<p>May 1, 2024</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.window:window-*:1.3.0-beta02</code> is released. Version 1.3.0-beta02 contains <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/02b55f664eba38e42e362e1af3913be1df552d55..fbd1ac175922f44c69a13545d194066ee428b342/window\">these commits</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>API Changes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Remove support for creating and using custom <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">WindowSizeClass</code>'s. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/Id1143662800446f3868a5324a2f647956610a84e\">Id1143</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixes <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">KotlinReflectionInternalError</code> caused by proguard stripping out some files on certain device implementations. (<a href=\"https://android-review.git.corp.google.com/c/platform/frameworks/support/+/3059406\">I01b02</a>)</li>\n</ul>",
  "commitsUrl": "https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/02b55f664eba38e42e362e1af3913be1df552d55..fbd1ac175922f44c69a13545d194066ee428b342/window"
}